ar or outlined passthrough options) level with 7 types of animals", "short_description": "Create a Zoo in your home with over 7 animals in this demo! \n(full game has over 60 animals, with various sizes)\n- Demo of \"Animalz Mixed Reality\"\n- Demo: lion, elephant, T-Rex, turtle, stag (deer), crocodile, great white shark, fish, and hippo\n- move, delete animals\n- passthrough enabled: see animals in your surroundings in mixed reality\n- variety of customizable animal placement levels and animal sizes in full version, in the demo there is one level preset"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1819021644882647"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["DINOSAURS", "EDUCATIONAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8003740429745668"}, "review_messages": ["", "", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75195909_477039435108758_3813017641114219377_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gt4q3pdWqV8Q7kNvgGI2sRu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCgBTJJaW8l1-CvaqLFjYE2lBt1trK1MuWQXZ2C_F7XiQ&oe=6777C1DA"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid